        <p>You may or may not recall, that the competition to design the new GAWDS website was won by Phil Treble; I apologise to Phil that it has taken some time for the design to appear on the site. We spent a bit of extra time trying to make it as usable as accessible as we could (of course we thought it was darn good in the first place).</p>
